cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.IOT, cs.SY, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new framework for deep learning, which is the main focus of the paper. 
- cs.DB (Databases): The framework proposed in the paper uses databases to store and access data, which is a key component of the framework. 
- cs.IOT (Internet of Things): The paper applies the proposed framework to optimize the control of electrical power consumed by a massive internet of things network of retail refrigeration systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper focuses on optimizing the control of electrical power consumed by a network of refrigeration systems, which falls under the category of systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new framework for deep learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence.
